These are Puzzles for 4x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x7-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: bellflower, poppy, balloon-flower, daisy, azalea, dahlia, zinnia
7 different games are played: backgammon, poker, domino, scrabble, chess, mah-jongg, go
The people have 7 different hobbies: gardening, filmmaking, puzzles, rock-climbing, skydiving, fishing, woodworking
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, ship, subway, train, van
 1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
 2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person playing scrabble##1
 3. the person driving the subway is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 4. the person playing poker is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 5. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing go##1
 6. the person who growspoppy is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
 7. the person driving the van is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 8. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the van and the person playing mah-jongg##2
 9. the person playing chess is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person who growsballoon-flower is in the middle##1
11. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person who growsazalea##1
12. the person who growsazalea is the person driving the bike##1
13. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person playing domino##1
14. the person playing mah-jongg is the person driving the quad-bike##1
15. the person driving the train is on the left of the person playing go##1
16. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
17. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person playing domino##1
18. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person playing chess##1
19. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |    3     |     4      |     5     |    6     |    7    |
| Flower      | poppy  | dahlia        | azalea | balloon-flower      | daisy     | bellflower      | zinnia     |
| Game   | poker | scrabble         | go   | backgammon | mah-jongg    | chess | domino |
| Hobby         | puzzles | skydiving | gardening | filmmaking | woodworking  | fishing  | rock-climbing    |
| Transport     | subway  | train         | bike     | jet-ski    | quad-bike | ship     | van     |

