 3. the malaysian is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the dutch##1
 5. the malaysian is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the owner of the dog is on the left of the malaysian##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is the owner of the goldfish##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is the dutch##1
 9. the mexican is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
10. the person who's birthday is in december is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person eating strawberry##2
11. the person who's birthday is in february is the person eating pineapple##1
12. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
13. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person eating strawberry and the person who's birthday is in november##2
14. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the indian##1
15. the malaysian is on the right of the pakistani##1
16. the dutch is on the far left##1
17. the person eating apricot is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
18. the person eating artichoke is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
19. the indian is on the right of the italian##1
20. the person eating broccoli is between the malaysian and the person eating artichoke##2

